This paper deals with improving energy efficiency in femtocell networks, which is a topic related to network optimization and game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses game theory and reinforcement learning, which are topics related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which are topics related to control systems and systems engineering. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another likely category. Finally, the paper deals with signal-to-interference-plus-noise-ratio requirements, which is a topic related to information theory. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a likely category.
